<blockquote><strong>Pulse Specialists &amp; Plant Breeders</strong></blockquote>
<p>We are specialist producers of Pulses for food use around the world, and have produced this website as a guide and introduction to buyers, end users, advisors and growers of Peas and Beans, both in the UK and around the World.</p>
<p>With our Partners <a href="http://www.senova.uk.com/" target="_blank">Senova</a>, we have our own plant breeding programme which supports our innovative approach to product development and business outlook.</p>
<p>For more information please go to <a href="http://www.winter-beans.co.uk" target="_blank">www.winter-beans.co.uk</a></p>
<p>We are members of <a href="https://www.agindustries.org.uk/home/" target="_blank">AIC</a>, <a href="http://www.bepa.co.uk" target="_blank">BEPA</a> &amp; <a href="http://www.bspb.co.uk" target="_blank">BSPB</a>.</p>
<p>Please feel free to browse around our site and <a href="/index.php/contact">contact us</a> if you have any questions.</p>
